{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "10", "m": "03", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "03", "M": "58", "S": "06"}}, "news": [{"title": "Lucknow: 549 plots allotted under land pooling policy in LDA\u2019s IT City scheme", "para": "The Lucknow Development Authority (LDA) held a lottery to allot residential plots to farmers and landowners who contributed land for the IT City scheme.  The draw, streamed live, allocated 549 plots of various sizes in sectors 15, 16, 17, 18, and 30.  Around 350 landowners pooled nearly 550 acres for the project.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/residential/lda-allots-549-plots-to-farmers-under-it-city-land-pooling-policy/129368192?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-224838/129368192.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "residential"}, {"title": "CIDCO plans 120-acre commercial hub in Navi Mumbai, floats tender for 20-year development", "para": "CIDCO has invited bids to develop a 120-acre International Corporate Park in Navi Mumbai's Kharghar, aiming to create a new business district akin to BKC. This initiative, under the state's Theme-Based policy, seeks a private developer via competitive bidding to foster a world-class corporate ecosystem and boost Navi Mumbai's economic growth.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/commercial/cidco-unveils-ambitious-120-acre-corporate-hub-in-navi-mumbais-kharghar/129368051?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-179970/129368051.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "commercial"}, {"title": "Truhome Finance files \u20b93,000-crore IPO papers", "para": "Truhome Finance, backed by Warburg Pincus, is launching an IPO to raise Rs 3,000 crore. The housing finance company plans to use the funds to strengthen its capital base for future lending and meet regulatory requirements. This move